data.description: MLS# 272862 Welcome to 9003 Wellington Way in West Pasco. This beautiful 1 story with bonus sits on a large corner lot in the highly desired Broadmoor Estates neighborhood and is walking distance to Columbia River Elementary and Reynold Middle School. Pulling up, take notice of the meticulous landscaping and freshly painted exterior and shutters, making this home picture-perfect. As you step inside, you will be greeted by an abundance of natural light that highlights the tasteful finishes and attention to the new engineer hardwood floors. The open concept living area features natural light that floods the space, gas fireplace with tile surround, and door to your back patio. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with stainless steel appliances, 5-burner cooktop, wall oven, microwave, granite countertops, ample cabinetry, new dishwasher, island with breakfast bar, plus a wet bar to enjoy making cocktails or a coffee station. The dining area is perfect for hosting dinner parties or intimate gatherings. The primary suite is a peaceful retreat that features a luxurious ADA step-in jetted bath, separate tiled shower, a HUGE walk-in closet with custom shelving, and plenty of room to relax and unwind. The junior suite is a perfect guest room or can be used as a second primary bedroom, providing privacy and convenience for your guests with a full bathroom. There is a 3rd bedroom is close to the home’s main bathroom. The office is ideal for those who work from home or could be used as a 4th bedroom. The laundry room features a utility sink with drawer underneath for storage. Upstairs, the versatile bonus space can be used as a game room, a home theater, a second living area, or even an extra guest room. The possibilities are truly endless! Let's head outside to the fully fenced-in private backyard oasis that is perfect for outdoor entertaining or just relaxing in the sunshine. It features a large, covered patio, a spacious lawn, plenty of room for outdoor toys/games, raised boxed garden beds, and an oversized shed to store your lawn items or a future hobby space. The side double gate provides convenient access to the backyard. Additional features include tankless water heater, water softener, new HVAC Humidified, 2 car garage with parking out front for 3 cars, extra storage closet in garage, enclosed workout room or could be a workshop, and much more.
